{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":531,"text":"It was less than a year after September 11,"},{"time":3107,"text":"and I was at the Chicago Tribune"},{"time":4782,"text":"writing about shootings and murders,"},{"time":6656,"text":"and it was leaving me feeling"},{"time":8118,"text":"pretty dark and depressed."},{"time":9900,"text":"I had done some activism in college,"},{"time":11482,"text":"so I decided to help a local group"},{"time":13129,"text":"hang door knockers against animal testing."},{"time":15838,"text":"I thought it would be a safe way"},{"time":17345,"text":"to do something positive,"},{"time":19227,"text":"but of course I have the absolute worst luck ever,"},{"time":21793,"text":"and we were all arrested."},{"time":24118,"text":"Police took this blurry photo of me"},{"time":26330,"text":"holding leaflets as evidence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29556,"text":"My charges were dismissed,"},{"time":31420,"text":"but a few weeks later,"},{"time":32556,"text":"two FBI agents knocked on my door,"},{"time":34593,"text":"and they told me that unless I helped them"},{"time":36354,"text":"by spying on protest groups,"},{"time":38455,"text":"they would put me on a domestic terrorist list."},{"time":42272,"text":"I'd love to tell you that I didn't flinch,"},{"time":44308,"text":"but I was terrified,"},{"time":46299,"text":"and when my fear subsided,"},{"time":48183,"text":"I became obsessed with finding out"},{"time":50100,"text":"how this happened,"},{"time":51217,"text":"how animal rights and environmental activists"},{"time":53395,"text":"who have never injured anyone"},{"time":55609,"text":"could become the FBI's number one"},{"time":57522,"text":"domestic terrorism threat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60726,"text":"A few years later, I was invited to testify"},{"time":62696,"text":"before Congress about my reporting,"},{"time":65200,"text":"and I told lawmakers that, while everybody"},{"time":66558,"text":"is talking about going green,"},{"time":68283,"text":"some people are risking their lives"},{"time":69821,"text":"to defend forests and to stop oil pipelines."},{"time":73333,"text":"They're physically putting their bodies on the line"},{"time":75382,"text":"between the whalers' harpoons and the whales."},{"time":78807,"text":"These are everyday people,"},{"time":80496,"text":"like these protesters in Italy"},{"time":82582,"text":"who spontaneously climbed over"},{"time":84644,"text":"barbed wire fences to rescue beagles"},{"time":86945,"text":"from animal testing."},{"time":89106,"text":"And these movements have been incredibly effective"},{"time":91782,"text":"and popular,"},{"time":93720,"text":"so in 1985, their opponents made up a new word,"},{"time":97581,"text":"eco-terrorist,"},{"time":99145,"text":"to shift how we view them."},{"time":101269,"text":"They just made it up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103156,"text":"Now these companies have backed new laws"},{"time":105693,"text":"like the Animal Enterprise Terrorism Act,"},{"time":108432,"text":"which turns activism into terrorism"},{"time":110551,"text":"if it causes a loss of profits."},{"time":113319,"text":"Now most people never even heard about this law,"},{"time":116318,"text":"including members of Congress."},{"time":118444,"text":"Less than one percent were in the room"},{"time":120355,"text":"when it passed the House."},{"time":122815,"text":"The rest were outside at a new memorial."},{"time":125718,"text":"They were praising Dr. King"},{"time":127379,"text":"as his style of activism was branded as terrorism"},{"time":130805,"text":"if done in the name of animals or the environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134456,"text":"Supporters say laws like this are needed"},{"time":136393,"text":"for the extremists:"},{"time":138242,"text":"the vandals, the arsonists, the radicals."},{"time":141191,"text":"But right now, companies like TransCanada"},{"time":143453,"text":"are briefing police in presentations like this one"},{"time":146778,"text":"about how to prosecute nonviolent protesters"},{"time":149467,"text":"as terrorists."},{"time":151605,"text":"The FBI's training documents on eco-terrorism"},{"time":155228,"text":"are not about violence,"},{"time":156779,"text":"they're about public relations."},{"time":159492,"text":"Today, in multiple countries,"},{"time":161465,"text":"corporations are pushing new laws"},{"time":162953,"text":"that make it illegal to photograph"},{"time":164667,"text":"animal cruelty on their farms."},{"time":167927,"text":"The latest was in Idaho just two weeks ago,"},{"time":170454,"text":"and today we released a lawsuit"},{"time":172227,"text":"challenging it as unconstitutional"},{"time":173954,"text":"as a threat to journalism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176527,"text":"The first of these ag-gag prosecutions,"},{"time":178865,"text":"as they're called,"},{"time":180300,"text":"was a young woman named Amy Meyer,"},{"time":181952,"text":"and Amy saw a sick cow being moved"},{"time":183565,"text":"by a bulldozer outside of a slaughterhouse"},{"time":186114,"text":"as she was on the public street."},{"time":188528,"text":"And Amy did what any of us would:"},{"time":190739,"text":"She filmed it."},{"time":192514,"text":"When I found out about her story, I wrote about it,"},{"time":195563,"text":"and within 24 hours, it created such an uproar"},{"time":198488,"text":"that the prosecutors just dropped all the charges."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201738,"text":"But apparently, even exposing stuff like that"},{"time":203756,"text":"is a threat."},{"time":205576,"text":"Through the Freedom of Information Act,"},{"time":207240,"text":"I learned that the counter-terrorism unit"},{"time":209100,"text":"has been monitoring my articles"},{"time":211177,"text":"and speeches like this one."},{"time":213463,"text":"They even included this nice\nlittle write-up of my book."},{"time":215689,"text":"They described it as \"compelling and well-written.\""},{"time":218804,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":223525,"text":"Blurb on the next book, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226760,"text":"The point of all of this is to make us afraid,"},{"time":230400,"text":"but as a journalist, I have an unwavering faith"},{"time":232289,"text":"in the power of education."},{"time":234120,"text":"Our best weapon is sunlight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237687,"text":"Dostoevsky wrote that the whole work of man"},{"time":239574,"text":"is to prove he's a man and not a piano key."},{"time":242899,"text":"Over and over throughout history,"},{"time":244461,"text":"people in power have used fear"},{"time":246449,"text":"to silence the truth and to silence dissent."},{"time":250248,"text":"It's time we strike a new note."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252287,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254262,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}